# By default the external editor is not enabled.
run
key alt+f2
----
-- view:
> [7m [0m                                                                           â¤
M-? toggle key help â€¢ C-d erase/stop â€¢ C-c clear/cancel â€¢ M-. hide/show promptğŸ›‡

# But it can be enabled explicitly.
run
